        <bioghist id="ref7">
            <head>Biographical note</head>
            <p>Robert Michael Ballantyne (1825-1894) was a Scottish born novelist, primarily of juvenile literature. During the course of his literary career, he authored more than 100 books, including <title render="italic">The Coral Island</title> (1858) and <title render="italic">Snowflake and Sunbeams</title> (1856).</p>
        </bioghist>
        <scopecontent id="ref1">
